          Will I have permanent access to courses?
          <span class="text-mint-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">‚ñº</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="p-4 pt-0 text-white/70 border-t border-white/10 mt-2">
          Yes. Once you enroll in a course on Udemy (even with a free coupon), you have lifetime access to all course materials, videos, and downloads. This access never expires.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="group bg-white/5 rounded-lg border border-white/10 overflow-hidden">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 cursor-pointer hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors font-semibold text-white">
          How often are new coupons added?
          <span class="text-mint-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">‚ñº</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="p-4 pt-0 text-white/70 border-t border-white/10 mt-2">
          New coupons are added daily. Our team adds 15-30 fresh verified coupons every day, and we refresh all existing coupons weekly. Subscribe to our RSS feed for instant notifications of new deals.
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
